original_title: Golden Gate: Seduced by San Francisco
overview: Prepare to get Seduced by San Francisco and enter the land of impulse, dreams and desire with the third installment of Naked Sword's hit series Golden Gate. Eight guys... four hardcore sex scenes... seven incredible solos... and tons of bonus material. Golden Gate: Seduced by San Francisco is an exploration of the sex lives of gay men living in the famed locale. Each episode of Golden Gate is a well-crafted vignette that brings together two disparate elements of the city beloved by so many men. Voice Over: Chris Porter
tagline: This group of men lives in San Francisco and they get seduced by everyday ...
